title: No Wheat Banana Bread
directions: Place bananas, eggs, vanilla, honey and coconut oil in a food processor. Pulse ingredients together. Pulse in almond flour, salt and baking soda. Scoop batter into a greased 7.5" x 3.5" Loaf Pan. Bake at 350ÂºF for 55-65 minutes. Remove from oven and allow to cool before your family devours it!
Whenever we have this bread around my husband always opts to have it for breakfast with his tea. I love it as an afternoon snack and my 3 year old would choose to eat it all day long!
